name: The Gentlemen
overview: When aristocratic Eddie inherits the family estate, he discovers that it's home to an enormous weed empire — and its proprietors aren't going anywhere.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: When aristocratic Eddie inherits the family estate, he discovers that it's home to an enormous weed empire — and its proprietors aren't going anywhere.

episodes.name: Refined Aggression
episodes.overview: When the Duke of Halstead dies, his second son inherits everything, including the title, house and grounds — plus a whole heap of trouble.

episodes.name: Tackle Tommy Woo Woo
episodes.overview: The toffs and their gamekeeper hunt a new kind of prey. Susie enlists some help to clean up the mess, and Halstead Manor is blessed with a holy visitor.

episodes.name: Where's My Weed At?
episodes.overview: Jimmy gets distracted on the job. As supply chain issues delay deliveries, the Horniman brothers take a risky ride to placate a dissatisfied customer.

episodes.name: An Unsympathetic Gentleman
episodes.overview: Susie is keen to expand the business. Eddie is determined that it won't be on his estate, so the Hornimans search for alternative locations.

episodes.name: I've Hundreds of Cousins
episodes.overview: Distribution issues in Europe and a theft on the farm cause a headache for Eddie and Susie — until they make a new acquaintance who can help them out.

episodes.name: All Eventualities
episodes.overview: Eddie's doubts about Susie continue to grow. But there's 15 million pounds of dirty money to be laundered before she'll consider leaving the estate.

episodes.name: Not Without Danger
episodes.overview: Bent on vengeance, Susie goes against her father's orders. Eddie offers to help her but is less certain than ever about where his allegiances lie.

episodes.name: The Gospel According to Bobby Glass
episodes.overview: A familiar face returns to settle a score with Freddy. Bobby decides it's time to retire and wants Eddie and Susie to make the necessary arrangements.
